headline: Realty Income Announces 667th Consecutive Common Stock Monthly Dividend
summary: Realty Income Corporation (Realty Income, NYSE: O), The Monthly Dividend Company®, today announced that it has declared its 667th consecutive common stock monthly dividend. The dividend amount of $0.2700 per share, representing an annualized amount of $3.240 per share, is payable on February 13, 2026 to stockholders of record as of January 30, 2026.
